<br>
Pets get dual wield ability at level 24<br>
<br>
Pets Duel Wield without aid of Weapons at level 39, and also get a regen bonus. <br>
<br>
I take this to mean that weapons become irrelevant at 39, unless you are looking for a specific proc effect or stat modifier, Raz's earlier post has some good combo's.....<br>
<br>
To the orignal poster, who is level 31, keep on giving weapons to your pet to improve your # of attacks. <br>
<br>
Would there be a modern day difference between say Summon Fang, and Sword of Runes if you weren't fighting summoned creatures?<br>
<br>
<br>
Naladini<br>
